**Purpose**: Answer options for MCQ-type questions.

| Column | Type | Constraints | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `id` | `BIGINT UNSIGNED` | PK, AUTO_INCREMENT | |
| `question_id` | `BIGINT UNSIGNED` | FK → `quiz_questions.id`, ON DELETE CASCADE | |
| `option_text` | `VARCHAR(500)` | NOT NULL | The option content |
| `is_correct` | `BOOLEAN` | DEFAULT false | Marks the correct answer |
| `sort_order` | `INT` | DEFAULT 0 | |

**Indexes**: `question_id`

---

#### Table: `quiz_attempts`

**Purpose**: Records each time a student takes a quiz.

| Column | Type | Constraints | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| `id` | `BIGINT UNSIGNED` | PK, AUTO_INCREMENT | |
| `quiz_id` | `BIGINT UNSIGNED` | FK → `quizzes.id`, ON DELETE CASCADE | |
| `student_id` | `BIGINT UNSIGNED` | FK → `students.id`, ON DELETE CASCADE | |
| `score` | `DECIMAL(5,2)` | NULLABLE | Calculated after submission |
| `total_marks` | `INT` | NOT NULL | Snapshot of quiz total marks |
| `percentage` | `DECIMAL(5,2)` | NULLABLE | |
| `passed` | `BOOLEAN` | NULLABLE | Based on pass_percentage |
| `time_taken_seconds` | `INT` | NULLABLE | Actual time spent |
| `started_at` | `TIMESTAMP` | NOT NULL | |
| `submitted_at` | `TIMESTAMP` | NULLABLE | NULL = in progress |
| `created_at` | `TIMESTAMP` | | |

**Indexes**: `quiz_id`, `student_id`, composite [(quiz_id, student_id)](file:///c:/Flutter/edustream/lib/features/home/presentation/screens/home_screen.dart#36-71)

